        STRIPE_API_KEY= **
        NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=
        STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET = no terminal Ready! Your webhook signing secret is...
        STRIPE_SUCCESS_URL =http://localhost:3000/posts
        STRIPE_CANCEL_URL =http://localhost:3000/


        #GitHub
        GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=  **
